description:
Click/tap to start music
Click/tap and drag to interact
Best experienced with headphones.

///

"The world is full of resonances. It constitutes a cosmos of things exerting a spiritual action." ~ Wassily Kandinsky

Everything flows in waves and cycles. The points where these waves meet creates new patterns and counter-waves. Waves propagate from a source but cycles from an unknown source.

///

An interactive audiovisual piece. Clicking starts two loops: a bass line and a melody line. They occur in interfering rhythms. Each note flicks a resonant point in a random direction. The viewer can move the resonant points.

///

Made by Sam Tsao (@sam___tsao) with p5.js and Tone.js.
